## Project Structure
<!-- Key directories Claude should know about; omit irrelevant ones -->
- `src/components/` — UI components
- `src/composables/` — shared logic / hooks
- `src/api/` — API route handlers
- `src/stores/` — state management (Pinia / Redux / Zustand)
- `tests/` — test files (mirrors src/ structure)
<!-- Add or remove entries to match the actual layout -->

## Conventions
<!-- Project-specific coding standards that go beyond L1/L2 rules -->
<!-- Only include things that differ from the company-wide default -->
- Component naming: PascalCase
- File naming: kebab-case
- Imports: use path aliases (`@/components/...`)
- {e.g., "Always use <script setup> in Vue SFCs"}
- {e.g., "Prefer named exports; avoid default exports"}

## Testing
<!-- How Claude should run tests for this project -->
- Run tests: `pnpm test`
- Coverage threshold: {e.g., 60%}
- Coverage command: `pnpm test:coverage`
- Run from: {e.g., repo root, or `apps/main/` if monorepo}
<!-- Note any special setup required before running tests, e.g. "requires .env.local" -->

## Development
<!-- Common commands Claude may need during implementation -->
- Dev server: `pnpm dev`
- Build: `pnpm build`
- Lint: `pnpm lint`
- Type-check: `pnpm typecheck`
